abstract: Bo K. Brownstein, the head of Big 5 Asset Management and a former banker at Credit Suisse in New York, is expected to admit to trading on a confidential stock tip.
snippet: Bo K. Brownstein, the head of Big 5 Asset Management and a former banker at Credit Suisse in New York, is expected to admit to trading on a confidential stock tip.

headline.main: Hedge Fund Manager Expected to Plead Guilty to Insider Trading
headline.print_headline: Fund Manager Is Said to Accept Guilty Plea on Insider Charges
